data.description: Situated on a generous lot, this stunning residence boasts breathtaking mountain views, no maintenance front yard and oasis style backyard landscaping, creates a SERENE retreat for everyday living and entertaining alike. The meticulously manicured grounds feature a PRIVATE POOL and spa, ideal for RELAXING under the warm California sun or hosting unforgettable gatherings with FRIENDS and FAMILY. A large MASTER SUITE provides access directly to the pool, while additional bedrooms offer COMFORT and privacy for guests or family members, while VERSATILE bonus spaces provide endless possibilities for customization to suit your lifestyle needs. Whether you're looking to move into an established community or investing into a DESERT RETREAT, this house will allow you to make in a home you always wanted. Conveniently located near shopping, dining, and entertainment options, as well as prestigious golf courses and outdoor recreation areas, 31260 Avenida Valdez presents an unparalleled opportunity to experience the quintessential California lifestyle.
